# RQ-53-10-01-002: Limit Load 2.5g

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone structure shall withstand limit load factor of 2.5g without permanent deformation.

## Rationale
Per CS-25.303, limit load represents the maximum anticipated load in service. Structure must remain elastic (no permanent deformation) at this load level.

